    "title": {
      "rendered": "3 Smart Branding Strategies for Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<h6>By <span style=\"color: #3b78dd;\"><a style=\"color: #3b78dd;\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/bethsinger1/\">Beth Singer</a></span>, Principal at <a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><span style=\"color: #3b78dd;\">Beth Singer Design, LLC</span></a> \u2013 a design and communications firm specializing in nonprofit organizations to help them fundraise, educate, and promote membership and events through design solutions.</h6>\n<hr />\n<p>As passionate as we all are about our causes and their corresponding missions, from the inside looking out, sometimes we lose sight of the actual goal of our communications. As we develop branded products, we may find ourselves bending to internal politics or the influence of a board member, or maybe we strive too hard be diplomatic. And often we overexplain!</p>\n<p>Since we all spend a lot of effort creating emails, posting on social media, blogging, and producing printed content, don\u2019t we want to make sure our communications are highly functioning and credible? If so, we must be disciplined about WHY we are generating all this content and going through the gyrations of pushing it out to constituents. What, exactly, are we trying to get them to do, think, or feel?</p>\n<p>A good place to start is by making sure that our communications and branding fulfill one or more of the following goals:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Move people to a specific action</li>\n<li>Motivate people to donate</li>\n<li>Educate</li>\n</ul>\n<p>So, what\u2019s the secret sauce?</p>\n<p><strong>Demonstrate that <em>your</em> values are <em>their</em> values. Create an emotional connection with your target audience to bring them closer to your cause.</strong></p>\n<p>Here are three strategic practices for connecting more deeply with your constituents. These practices are quintessential ways to turn interested parties into devoted advocates, action-oriented followers, and committed donors.</p>\n<h2><strong>1) Stay on point. Clearly and simply define the purpose of the communication.</strong></h2>\n<p>Do you want them to become a member? Know more about the issues so that they become advocates for your mission? Feel connected to your organization through financial commitment or volunteering their time? Every project decision should distinctly support the goal, which can mean being ruthless as you decide what to keep and what to let go.</p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #3b78dd;\"><a style=\"color: #3b78dd;\" href=\"https://www.jewishfederations.org/\">Jewish Federations of North America</a></span><br />\nMake a Blessing/Be a Blessing Campaign</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29644\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/JFED-24-Banner-700x525-1.jpg?resize=700%2C525\" alt=\"\" width=\"700\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/JFED-24-Banner-700x525-1.jpg?w=700&amp;ssl=1 700w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/JFED-24-Banner-700x525-1.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29645\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-Blessings-1024x652.jpg?resize=960%2C611\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"611\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-Blessings.jpg?resize=1024%2C652&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-Blessings.jpg?resize=300%2C191&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-Blessings.jpg?resize=768%2C489&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-Blessings.jpg?w=1240&amp;ssl=1 1240w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29646\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/JFED-Email-CropA-958x1024.jpg?resize=958%2C1024\" alt=\"\" width=\"958\" height=\"1024\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/JFED-Email-CropA.jpg?resize=958%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 958w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/JFED-Email-CropA.jpg?resize=281%2C300&amp;ssl=1 281w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/JFED-Email-CropA.jpg?resize=768%2C821&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/JFED-Email-CropA.jpg?w=1193&amp;ssl=1 1193w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 958px) 100vw, 958px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Here is a laser-focused fundraising appeal that centers around the blessings of Hanukkah and a shared belief that deep down each of us can provide comfort to someone else. The products (shown above are a social media graphic, print ads, and an email) were created for the regional offices of The Jewish Federation of North America. Nationwide, 56 Federation offices downloaded the outreach materials and templates 467 times.</p>\n<h2><strong>2) Use your brand smartly and consistently.</strong></h2>\n<p>Look at your brand attributes without bias. Do they convey the values and messages that reflect your organization and its mission? Think of your logo, tagline, typefaces, and design treatments as the \u201cuniform\u201d your organization always wears. By appearing in uniform, your communications become part of a team that stands out from a crowd. If your social media, email, website, and print collateral are consistent, they add up to a whole, rather than remaining isolated and lost as opportunities to communicate your core messages. And equally important, consistent and smart use of your brand reflects the organization\u2019s efficiency, thoughtfulness, and attention to detail \u2014 something your supporters will care about.</p>\n<p>Expressing that <em>your</em> values are <em>their</em> values spotlights the ideas and beliefs you have in common.</p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #3b78dd;\"><a style=\"color: #3b78dd;\" href=\"https://www.cbsteaneck.org/\">Congregation Beth Shalom</a></span><br />\nBranding</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29664\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-CBSLogo-1024x768.jpg?resize=960%2C720\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-CBSLogo.jpg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-CBSLogo.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-CBSLogo.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-CBSLogo.jpg?w=1500&amp;ssl=1 1500w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29665\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan-1024x1024.jpg?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-Susan.jpg?w=1080&amp;ssl=1 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29666\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB-1024x1024.jpg?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaB.jpg?w=1080&amp;ssl=1 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29667\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC-1024x1024.jpg?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-SocialGraphic-MichaC.jpg?w=1080&amp;ssl=1 1080w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29669\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding3-1024x713.jpg?resize=960%2C668\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"668\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding3.jpg?resize=1024%2C713&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding3.jpg?resize=300%2C209&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding3.jpg?resize=768%2C535&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding3.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29670\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding4-1024x713.jpg?resize=960%2C668\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"668\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding4.jpg?resize=1024%2C713&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding4.jpg?resize=300%2C209&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding4.jpg?resize=768%2C535&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/CBS-Social-Branding4.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This congregation in New Jersey was unique in what it offered \u2014 a vibrant and relevant form of traditional Judaism, a lifestyle of learning and holiday observance, and a warm and inclusive community. Their key messages were built into the tagline \u2014 <em>Jewish Life, Inspired.</em> Shown above are the logo, social media \u201cstory\u201d posts, and postcards, which originally introduced the brand. All communications for the organization consistently center around the inspirational nature of the community. See more at <a href=\"http://www.cbsteaneck.org\"><strong>cbsteaneck.org</strong></a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CBSTeaneck\"><strong>on Facebook @CBSTeaneck</strong></a>. Since its inception, the new brand has attracted 30 new families to the synagogue and coalesced the existing members around the clearly articulated, distinguishing features of the community.</p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.alyn.org/\">ALYN Hospital</a><br />\nWheels of Love Branding and Recruitment</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29674\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b-1024x1024.jpg?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March1b.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29675\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a-1024x1024.jpg?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3a.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29676\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b-1024x1024.jpg?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March2b.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29677\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b-1024x1024.jpg?resize=960%2C960\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b.jpg?resize=1024%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b.jpg?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-SocialPost-March3b.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<div style=\"width: 960px;\" class=\"wp-video\"><video class=\"wp-video-shortcode\" id=\"video-29641-3\" width=\"960\" height=\"960\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\"><source type=\"video/mp4\" src=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Movie1-1080p.mp4?_=3\" /><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Movie1-1080p.mp4\">http://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Movie1-1080p.mp4</a></video></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29680\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Email1-SQ.png?resize=598%2C599\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"599\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Email1-SQ.png?w=598&amp;ssl=1 598w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Email1-SQ.png?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Email1-SQ.png?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Email1-SQ.png?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Email1-SQ.png?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/ALYN-Email1-SQ.png?resize=80%2C80&amp;ssl=1 80w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 598px) 100vw, 598px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ALYN is a world-class hospital in Israel dedicated to the rehabilitation of permanently and temporarily disabled children. Shown here are branded recruitment social media posts and email for this inaugural U.S.-based charity bike ride. The branding focuses on the main value the riders and hospital have in common \u2014 \u201cdoing good\u201d is a top priority for them. The ride quickly smashed its goal of 100 registrants in the first six weeks of the campaign.</p>\n<h2><strong>3) Speak the language of your community. Remember the people you are speaking to are far beyond the room.</strong></h2>\n<p>Do your homework and learn what keeps them up at night. Through personal interviews, surveys, and observing your supporters and community, you will have concrete data about their mindset and motivations for feeling \u2014 and acting \u2014 the way they do. No guesswork required! Make every effort to connect with those important feelings and belief systems you\u2019ve observed. Lay out a vision, both in words and in visuals, that speaks to the essence of the world they\u2019d like to see.</p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #3b78dd;\"><a style=\"color: #3b78dd;\" href=\"https://www.nif.org/\">New Israel Fund</a></span><br />\nPlanned Giving Campaign</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29686\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF40-TwoCovers-1024x853.jpg?resize=960%2C800\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF40-TwoCovers.jpg?resize=1024%2C853&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF40-TwoCovers.jpg?resize=300%2C250&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF40-TwoCovers.jpg?resize=768%2C640&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF40-TwoCovers.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29687\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-2-1024x768.jpg?resize=960%2C720\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-2.jpg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-2.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-2.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-2.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-29688\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-3-1024x768.jpg?resize=960%2C720\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-3.jpg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-3.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-3.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/NIF-40Brochure-3.jpg?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<p>This planned giving campaign for the New Israel Fund lays out a future that potential donors yearn to see \u2014 equal rights for all Israeli citizens. Infused with powerful words and provocative photos, readers understand that they can support NIF\u2019s important work that is consistent with their ideals, well beyond their lifetimes. Shown here are two brochures \u2014 one for mail and the other for in-person meetings. The campaign met its initial target of $40M and has extended its goal to $50M.</p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"https://healthinharmony.org/\">Health in Harmony</a><br />\nDonor Digital Presentation for Small Gatherings</strong></h6>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29695\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Speaking.jpg?resize=797%2C447\" alt=\"\" width=\"797\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Speaking.jpg?w=797&amp;ssl=1 797w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Speaking.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Speaking.jpg?resize=768%2C431&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 797px) 100vw, 797px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29696\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Speaking-empathyHiHb.jpg?resize=795%2C446\" alt=\"\" width=\"795\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Speaking-empathyHiHb.jpg?w=795&amp;ssl=1 795w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Speaking-empathyHiHb.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Speaking-empathyHiHb.jpg?resize=768%2C431&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 795px) 100vw, 795px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29697\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-HiHa.jpg?resize=796%2C446\" alt=\"\" width=\"796\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-HiHa.jpg?w=796&amp;ssl=1 796w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-HiHa.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-HiHa.jpg?resize=768%2C430&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 796px) 100vw, 796px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29698\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-HiHb.jpg?resize=798%2C447\" alt=\"\" width=\"798\" height=\"447\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-HiHb.jpg?w=798&amp;ssl=1 798w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-HiHb.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Blog-Branding-HiHb.jpg?resize=768%2C430&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 798px) 100vw, 798px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Health in Harmony\u2019s digital presentation focuses on environmental concerns and, by default, healthcare. It educates and builds a case for supporting HIH\u2019s work to restore the rainforests by helping the adjacent and indigenous populations with their reasons for cutting down the trees in the first place \u2014 access to affordable and quality healthcare.</p>\n<p>In short, your brand is an important and strategic tool to bring people closer to your organization. Applied simply and consistently \u2014 <em>and with discipline </em>\u2014 your brand will create that critical connection to your audience by promising them that your organization can be trusted with their attention, their time, and their financial support.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/bethsinger1/\"><span style=\"color: #3b78dd;\">Beth Singer</span></a> </strong>is Principal at <span style=\"color: #3b78dd;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #3b78dd;\" href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\">Beth Singer Design, LLC</a></strong></span> \u2013 a design and communications firm specializing in nonprofit organizations to help them fundraise, educate, and promote membership and events through design solutions.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.bethsingerdesign.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-29700\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Beth-Singer.jpg?resize=960%2C781\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"781\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Beth-Singer.jpg?w=978&amp;ssl=1 978w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Beth-Singer.jpg?resize=300%2C244&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/Beth-Singer.jpg?resize=768%2C625&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n",
